00:24:12.540 --> 00:24:15.420
Once you realize that
you're not the only one that

00:24:15.420 --> 00:24:18.640
loves this app or feels
this way about the game.

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:21.985
These are the experiences
that drive community.

00:24:21.985 --> 00:24:23.610
Experiences like the
one that we're all

00:24:23.610 --> 00:24:25.260
having now, where
you can connect

00:24:25.260 --> 00:24:28.530
with the people around you
over the idea of connecting

00:24:28.530 --> 00:24:31.695
with people is a
task worth taking on.

00:24:31.695 --> 00:24:34.070
And so what should you do
after you leave the room today?

00:24:37.590 --> 00:24:41.790
Bring back mindsets,
not tactics.

00:24:41.790 --> 00:24:44.640
Think about how you can bring
these into your work every day.

00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:47.370
We've introduced the
questions about how

00:24:47.370 --> 00:24:50.250
to create those spaces to
inspire people to reach

00:24:50.250 --> 00:24:54.720
beyond themselves, and asking
if this is the kind of work that

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:57.480
will move toward those places
where relationships can really

00:24:57.480 --> 00:24:59.800
thrive.

00:24:59.800 --> 00:25:02.820
And as you do that, I want to
